cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.EC, cs.IT 

The paper deals with a mechanism design problem, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves optimization and decision-making (cs.DS), as well as algorithms and computational complexity (cs.AI). The concept of auctions and revenue maximization falls under the category of computational economics (cs.EC), and the use of linear programming is a common tool in information theory (cs.IT).
